message.content:
Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.1">
    <title>AI Code Store - Cyberpunk</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset base */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: #000;
            color: #00-cyan;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(00, 00, 00, 0.8);
            border: 2 solid #0ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20 #0ff, inset 0 0 20 #0ff;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10;
            backdrop-filter: blur(3);
            animation: flicker 2s infinite alternate;
}

        @keyframes flicker {
        from {
            box-shadow: 0 0 5 #cyan, 0 0 10 #cyan, 0 0 20 #cyan;
        }
        to {
            box-shadow: 0 0 10 #cyan, 0 0 20 #cyan, 0 0 30 #cyan;
        }
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10 #cyan, 0 0 20 #cyan;
        letter-spacing: 4;
        margin-bottom: 0.5;
        color: #fff;
        border-bottom: 2 solid #0ff;
        padding-bottom: 10;
        display: inline-block;
        }

        .sub-title {
            color: #0ff;
            font-size: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 2;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 20, 0.5);
            border: 1 solid #cyan;
            padding: 1.5;
            border-radius: 8;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5 rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transition: 0.3;
        }

        .card:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5 #cyan;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2 solid #0ff;
            color: #0ff;
            padding: 0.8 2;
            font-size: 1.2;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2;
            margin-top: 1;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #0ff;
            color: #000;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10 #0ff;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.2;
        }

        input, textarea {
            background: #000;
            border: 1 solid #0ff;
            padding: 0.8;
            color: #0ff;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1;
            outline: none;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 5 #0ff;
        }

        label {
            color: #0ff;
            font-size: 0.9;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2;
            border-top: 1 solid #0ff;
            padding-top: 1;
            color: #888;
        }

        .popup-over {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(2);
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .popup-box {
            background: #000;
            border: 2 solid #0ff;
            padding: 2.5 3;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30 #0ff;
            animation: flicker 1.5 infinite;
        }

        .popup-box h2 {
            color: #0ff;
            font-size: 2;
            margin-bottom: 0.5;
        }

        .popup-box p {
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .popup-box .btn {
            margin-top: 1.5;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600) {
            .grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        }
    </style>
    <!-- Script -->
    <script>
        function mostraPopup() {
            document.getElementById('popup-over').display: block;
        }
        function nasodi() {
            document.getElementById('popup-over').display: none;
        }
        function inv() {
            // mostraPopup();
            // alert "richiesta inviata"
            // qui' eventuale invio form
            // per mostrare popup
            mostraPopup();
            // reset form (facile)
            document.getElementById('form').reset();
            // rest
            return false; // evita submit
        }
    </script>
    <!-- HTML -->
    <!-- /cor del container -->
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>AI Code Store</h1>
            <p class="sub-title">Negozio di programmazione AI - Cyberpunk</p>
        </header>
        <section class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>�DAI�BRA</h3>
